          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until fragrant</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse the<strong> butter beans</strong></p>",
